<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 20:07:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列认为哈马斯袭击后失踪的一些人将无法找到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-some-of-those-missing-after-hamas-attack-will-not-be-found/0000018b-4942-d5d2-afef-cdff5b7f0000</link><description>根据以色列国防军的最新数据，有 100 至 200 人被列为失踪人员，随着以色列继续寻找尸体，这一数字预计会发生变化。据军方了解，约有 30 名 16 岁以下儿童被绑架</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 19:57:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-some-of-those-missing-after-hamas-attack-will-not-be-found/0000018b-4942-d5d2-afef-cdff5b7f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正式加入美国免签证计划，立即生效</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-officially-in-the-u-s-visa-waiver-program-effective-immediately/0000018b-4972-d5d2-afef-cdffdb9a0000</link><description>以色列入境原定于 11 月 30 日开始，但由于哈马斯袭击后美国驻以色列大使馆暂停签证处理，迫于国会压力，这一进程已加快。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 19:41:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-officially-in-the-u-s-visa-waiver-program-effective-immediately/0000018b-4972-d5d2-afef-cdffdb9a0000</guid></item><item><title>2007年的内塔尼亚胡：总理对国家安全负有个人责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-in-2007-the-prime-minister-bears-personal-responsibility-for-national-security/0000018b-491b-d1fd-a59f-ed9b113e0000</link><description>“在像以色列这样的国家，如果一个人不具备某种塑造外交安全概念的能力，你就不能任命他为总理，因为如果是这样，那么这些机构就真正具有统治力；内塔尼亚胡向一个正在调查 2006 年第二次黎巴嫩战争的委员会作证说：“他不控制这些机构，也不指导它们”</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 18:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-in-2007-the-prime-minister-bears-personal-responsibility-for-national-security/0000018b-491b-d1fd-a59f-ed9b113e0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人没有安全的地方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/there-is-no-safe-place-for-the-jews/0000018b-487b-d03a-afcb-697b23400000</link><description>以色列最伟大的成就之一是它为本国公民以及世界各地的犹太人提供的安全和繁荣，让他们偶尔忘记自己面临着犹太人的仇恨。从以色列南部到澳大利亚悉尼，情况已不再如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 17:23:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/there-is-no-safe-place-for-the-jews/0000018b-487b-d03a-afcb-697b23400000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在安曼举行的中东峰会可能已取消，但美国仍应采取严肃的外交行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/bidens-summit-in-amman-may-have-been-cancelled-but-the-u-s-should-still-pursue-diplomacy/0000018b-489b-d1fd-a59f-ed9bf1a10000</link><description>拜登等美国总统周三的访问可能会成为中东外交的一个重大转折点，但问题是这是否是白宫想要的</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 16:44:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/bidens-summit-in-amman-may-have-been-cancelled-but-the-u-s-should-still-pursue-diplomacy/0000018b-489b-d1fd-a59f-ed9bf1a10000</guid></item><item><title>“我没有时间哀悼母亲被杀，因为我必须拯救孩子们的生命”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-dont-have-time-to-mourn-my-mothers-murder-because-i-have-to-save-my-childrens-life/0000018b-488d-d03a-afcb-69bf4ff60000</link><description>被哈马斯绑架进入加沙地带的儿童家属召开新闻发布会，恳求内塔尼亚胡、以色列政府和国际社会帮助释放人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 16:41:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-dont-have-time-to-mourn-my-mothers-murder-because-i-have-to-save-my-childrens-life/0000018b-488d-d03a-afcb-69bf4ff60000</guid></item><item><title>共和党人将呼吁加沙停火的犹太抗议者与 1 月 6 日的叛乱分子进行了比较</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/gop-compares-jewish-protesters-calling-for-gaza-cease-fire-to-january-6-insurrectionists/0000018b-481d-d242-abef-5a3f310d0000</link><description>众议员马乔里·泰勒·格林（Marjorie Taylor Greene）是支持特朗普的支持者之一，呼吁将周三在国会办公室静坐的数百名美国犹太抗议者“关押在华盛顿特区的古拉格集中营”，将他们的行为等同于所给予的治疗致 2021 年袭击国会大厦的人们</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 15:52:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/gop-compares-jewish-protesters-calling-for-gaza-cease-fire-to-january-6-insurrectionists/0000018b-481d-d242-abef-5a3f310d0000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德囚犯交换专家警告说，“释放以色列人质的机会之窗正在关闭”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/window-of-opportunity-to-free-israeli-hostages-is-closing-we-have-a-week/0000018b-482f-d5d2-afef-ccff4a650000</link><description>沙利特囚犯交换背后的摩萨德资深人士大卫·梅丹认为，哈马斯有兴趣迅速达成协议，释放被俘的以色列儿童、妇女和老人。他警告说，如果我们等到战后，许多人质将不再活着。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 15:50:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/window-of-opportunity-to-free-israeli-hostages-is-closing-we-have-a-week/0000018b-482f-d5d2-afef-ccff4a650000</guid></item><item><title>NSO 和以色列网络公司帮助追踪失踪的以色列人和人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cyber-arms-and-intelligence-firms-like-nso-aiding-israeli-efforts/0000018b-4813-de3d-a58f-c87b7d950000</link><description>从面部识别到开源情报和进攻性网络，NSO、Rayzone 等公司以及 AnyVision 等公司帮助绘制和跟踪人质和伤亡人员的情况</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 14:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cyber-arms-and-intelligence-firms-like-nso-aiding-israeli-efforts/0000018b-4813-de3d-a58f-c87b7d950000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯大使将加沙暴力归咎于西方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/russian-ambassador-blames-west-for-gaza-violence/0000018b-4838-d5d2-afef-ccfd4f2c0000</link><description>俄罗斯驻以色列特使阿纳托利·维克托罗夫在俄罗斯官方媒体 RT 频道上谴责西方：“他们并不是真的想帮助制止暴力”</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 14:41:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/russian-ambassador-blames-west-for-gaza-violence/0000018b-4838-d5d2-afef-ccfd4f2c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会道德委员会因将加沙战争与大屠杀联系起来而暂停并扣留 MK 的薪酬</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/knesset-ethics-committee-suspends-docks-pay-of-mk-for-tying-gaza-war-to-holocaust/0000018b-4815-d614-abcf-e87795490000</link><description>奥弗·卡西夫 (MK Ofer Cassif) 在接受有关以色列与哈马斯战争的采访时将右翼财政部长斯莫特里奇提出的计划称为“最终解决方案”，因此将被扣掉 14 天的工资。卡西夫表示，这一决定是政治言论自由棺材上的一颗钉子</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 14:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/knesset-ethics-committee-suspends-docks-pay-of-mk-for-tying-gaza-war-to-holocaust/0000018b-4815-d614-abcf-e87795490000</guid></item><item><title>葡萄牙采取行动终止塞法迪犹太公民身份法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/portugal-moves-to-end-sephardi-jewish-citizenship-law/0000018b-4818-d614-abcf-e87ba3530000</link><description>继西班牙之后，葡萄牙政界人士旨在废除允许伊比利亚血统的犹太人获得公民身份的法律；到 2022 年底，约 75,000 人获得公民身份</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 13:53:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/portugal-moves-to-end-sephardi-jewish-citizenship-law/0000018b-4818-d614-abcf-e87ba3530000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔支持哈马斯后，国际社会施压要求卡塔尔取消世界游泳锦标赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2023-10-19/ty-article/intl-pressure-to-move-world-swimming-championships-from-qatar-after-support-for-hamas/0000018b-4788-d614-abcf-effb11960000</link><description>在卡塔尔发表支持哈马斯的声明后，呼吁世界水上运动联合会将所有水上运动的国际锦标赛迁至多哈</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 13:42:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2023-10-19/ty-article/intl-pressure-to-move-world-swimming-championships-from-qatar-after-support-for-hamas/0000018b-4788-d614-abcf-effb11960000</guid></item><item><title>在哈马斯与以色列的战争中，苏格兰领导人呼吁欢迎巴勒斯坦难民来到英国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/scotlands-leader-calls-to-welcome-palestinian-refugees-to-the-u-k-amid-hamas-israel-war/0000018b-4776-d614-abcf-ef7760540000</link><description>在埃及阻止巴勒斯坦人过境之际，在加沙有姻亲的苏格兰大臣敦促英国致力于难民计划：“你如此关心人权——好吧，你接受它们，”埃及官员说</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 12:08:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/scotlands-leader-calls-to-welcome-palestinian-refugees-to-the-u-k-amid-hamas-israel-war/0000018b-4776-d614-abcf-ef7760540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察局长：“那些认同加沙的人可以被巴士护送到那里”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-commissioner-those-who-identify-with-gaza-can-be-escorted-there-on-buses/0000018b-4735-df22-a5eb-4f7dca0c0000</link><description>周三，数十名警察强行驱散海法的示威活动，警察局长科比·沙卜泰宣布警方不会允许声援加沙地带的示威活动</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 10:42:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-commissioner-those-who-identify-with-gaza-can-be-escorted-there-on-buses/0000018b-4735-df22-a5eb-4f7dca0c0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯、战争及其后果：我是以色列迷失的一代的一部分</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-war-and-the-aftermath-i-am-part-of-israels-lost-generation/0000018b-429d-d259-a3bb-cebf36f90000</link><description>我们是在内塔尼亚胡、恐怖袭击和占领的陪伴下长大的。我们被告知与巴勒斯坦人的冲突可以得到“控制”。哈马斯杀害了我们数百人，现在我们是战争中的应征入伍者。如果冲突没有结束的希望，我们的未来会怎样？</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 10:20:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-war-and-the-aftermath-i-am-part-of-israels-lost-generation/0000018b-429d-d259-a3bb-cebf36f90000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯绑架的以色列人家属对向加沙提供人道主义援助的决定感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israelis-kidnapped-by-hamas-angry-at-decision-to-provide-aid-to-gaza/0000018b-46c4-de3d-a58f-ceed160e0000</link><description>这些家人要求建立人道主义走廊，为人质提供药品，并改善与政府的沟通。一位亲戚说：“我们很震惊地听到人道主义援助正在转移给加沙居民。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 09:53:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israelis-kidnapped-by-hamas-angry-at-decision-to-provide-aid-to-gaza/0000018b-46c4-de3d-a58f-ceed160e0000</guid></item><item><title>突尼斯历史悠久的犹太教堂在与以色列-哈马斯战争有关的骚乱中严重受损</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/historic-synagogue-in-tunisia-heavily-damaged-in-rioting-tied-to-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-46c4-de3d-a58f-ceed15d90000</link><description>加沙医院爆炸后，数百人在反以色列骚乱期间纵火焚烧突尼斯中部城市哈马一座 16 世纪的犹太教堂</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 09:23:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/historic-synagogue-in-tunisia-heavily-damaged-in-rioting-tied-to-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-46c4-de3d-a58f-ceed15d90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列死者：在哈马斯袭击、屠杀和以色列-哈马斯战争中丧生的人的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/victims/0000018b-325c-d450-a3af-7b5cf0210000</link><description>超过 1,300 名以色列人、平民和士兵在家中、社区以及与哈马斯恐怖分子的对抗中丧生。以下是官方确认的 10 月 7 日暴行以及随后的以色列-哈马斯战争中丧生的以色列人姓名</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 09:00:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/victims/0000018b-325c-d450-a3af-7b5cf0210000</guid></item><item><title>只有拜登才能给以色列人带来他们想要的新希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/only-biden-can-give-israelis-the-fresh-hope-they-want/0000018b-426d-d881-abab-efeddfc90000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 07:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/only-biden-can-give-israelis-the-fresh-hope-they-want/0000018b-426d-d881-abab-efeddfc90000</guid></item></channel></rss>